<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٢ - تَمْرَةٌ خَيْرٌ مِنْ جَرَادَةٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>جَاءَ عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ أَنَّهُ سُئِلَ عَنْ صَيْدِ الْمُحْرِمِ يَصِيدُ الْجَرَادَ فَقَالَهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١٣ - تَمْكُثُ إِحْدَاكُنَّ شَطْرَ دَهْرِهَا لَا تُصَلِّي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَالَ النَّوَوِيُّ بَاطِلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>